[00:59.67]	'O, bless my brother!' Husband win, win brother,
[01:03.38]	Prays, and destroys the prayer; no midway
[01:06.87]	'Twixt these extremes at all.
[01:09.45]MARK ANTONY	Gentle Octavia,
[01:11.04]	Let your best love draw to that point, which seeks
[01:15.29]	Best to preserve it: if I lose mine honour,
[01:18.93]	I lose myself: better I were not yours
[01:22.26]	Than yours so branchless. But, as you requested,
[01:26.21]	Yourself shall go between 's: the mean time, lady,
[01:30.23]	I'll raise the preparation of a war
[01:33.41]	Shall stain your brother: make your soonest haste;
